item.title: IBRX
item.description: score:152 Chances: ImmunityBio, Inc. continues to make significant progress in its clinical-stage immunotherapy treatments, with positive interim results from the QUILT 3.032 study of N-803 plus BCG in BCG-unresponsive non-muscle invasive bladder cancer (NMIBC) and timely completion of its Biologics License Application (BLA) resubmission for FDA review.
